---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
const title = "Terms and Conditions | Innovate-X";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-800 font-sans">
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">Effective Date: June 18, 2025</p>

      <p class="mb-4">
        By registering for or participating in Innovate-X 2025, you agree to the
        following terms and conditions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Event Registration</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Registration is required through our Google Form. Please ensure all
        information is accurate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2. Eligibility</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Open to individuals interested in tech. You must be 16 years or older or
        have parental consent to participate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
        3. Changes and Cancellations
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We reserve the right to modify the schedule, speakers, or venue. If the
        event is canceled, we will notify you via the contact information
        provided.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Code of Conduct</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        All attendees must act respectfully. Harassment or disruptive behavior
        will result in removal from the event.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
        5. Use of Photos and Videos
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        By attending, you consent to photos or recordings that may be used for
        promotional purposes. To opt out, contact us beforehand.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
        6. Disclaimer of Liability
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We are not responsible for any injury, loss, or damage incurred during
        the event. Attendance is at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        For questions, contact us at: <strong
          ><a href="mailto:olakadasamuel@gmail.com">olakadasamuel@gmail.com</a
          ></strong
        >
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</Layout>
